								<li><strong>Backend - </strong>Java Spring Microservice architecture</li>
								<li><strong>Database - </strong>Large-scale data storage with MongoDB and PostgreSQL</li>
								<li><strong>Services - </strong>Multiple internal and external GET / POST service calls</li>
								<li><strong>Docker - </strong>Multiple Docker pods – each handling part of the system</li>
								<li><strong>Crawler - </strong>Customized web-crawler loading and parsing HTML content</li>
								<li><strong>WebSockets - </strong>Fast client / server communication using WebSockets</li>
							</ul>
